Copyright: 2015-2025 Brian Smith
License: ISC
Comment:
 The voisu, voisu-daemon and voisu-overlay binaries statically link the *ring*
 crate for TLS cryptography. New *ring* code is under this ISC-style license.
 ring's license texts ship under their UPSTREAM tree layout so that the
 cross-references inside ring's own LICENSE manifest resolve. ring/LICENSE is
 the upstream overview file; ring/LICENSE-other-bits carries the ISC text. Both
 are installed as /usr/share/doc/voisu/ring/LICENSE and
 /usr/share/doc/voisu/ring/LICENSE-other-bits.

